{"tid":1492032,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"F-16V亞洲最強中輕型戰機","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T15:59:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9acd24517bfb7d068efe6388877b9c643139e7d8","tid":1492032,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:55:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190820/20752293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190820%2F20752293&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41A%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=fb17016d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190820%2F20752293&h=f18e93e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190820/20752293</a><br />\n<br />\nF-16V亞洲最強中輕型戰機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190820/large/1566230922_bc16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190820%2Flarge%2F1566230922_bc16.jpg&h=8053a59d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由台軍既有F-16A/B戰機升級的F-16V戰機，今年5月在彰化舉行的「漢光35號」演習首次公開亮相。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這次特朗普批准售台的F-16V戰機，由美國軍工企業洛歇馬丁（Lockheed Martin）公司生產，是現役西方戰鬥機產量最大F-16戰機升級版，其中的「V」是viper（蝮蛇）的縮寫。F-16V被稱為是「亞洲最強中輕型戰機」，具備短途起降、部份隱匿和視距外導彈接戰能力，在一定條件下，可對大陸「殲20」戰機構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n台灣國防部智庫、國防安全研究院資源與產業研究所長蘇紫雲表示，F-16V所搭載的APG-83電子掃描陣列雷達（AESA），可同時執行搜索、追蹤並鎖定多目標；另外，改裝新式的電腦、座艙儀表、具備「看到哪、打到哪」的頭盔瞄準系統等，可搭配新一代AIM-9X響尾蛇導彈，戰力大躍進。F-16V引擎較舊款多出18%的推力，可協助F-16V縮短起飛距離50米以上（舊型起飛距離約520米），同時可提高爬升率至每秒260米，減輕幻影戰機高空攔截負擔。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：共66架 大幅提升防衞能力特朗普開綠燈 批准對台售F-16V<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新規劃應對大陸<br />\n<br />\n台灣軍方正規劃把位於台東的「空軍第七飛行訓練聯隊」遷移，並成立新的「空軍第七戰術戰鬥機聯隊」，以應對大陸解放軍威脅；另外戰時還可將F-16V戰機推入台東基地內的「建安」地下洞庫內，新機預計2024年可分批返台，強化台灣東南空域的空防戰力。台軍目前的F-16A/B型戰機早已老化。<br />\n<br />\n中央社 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n共66架大幅提升防衞能力 特朗普開綠燈批准對台售F-16V<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n蔡支持度大幅拋離韓7.8%"},{"pid":"e14adb989f09cc127e9bc40b1c10baff6e8cc02f","tid":1492032,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/20/233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F20%2F233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg&h=ba2d15e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0y2D12U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0y2D12U.jpg&h=c7bab806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYuV4gf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYuV4gf.jpg&h=52b2bc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tri4dee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftri4dee.png&h=7af3e96e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}